<br>
&quot;Hello Rollen. I have heard talk of this gnome illusion mask that you have and wish to hand out. I come to ask to be placed on the list for those that wish to have it. My purpose for it is simple. The much feared Dread Gnome Pirates is making its way more and more into Norrath and I need some way of infultrating their ranks. I have the habits and know their way of speech but I have a very difficult time getting deep into their lairs since my skin is so far from their skin color as well as my hair. I havent found the proper dyes and muds to sufficiently disguise myself. This mask would make my pilfering and spying much easier. Who knows, maybe I will become a Dread Gnome Pirate myself if they are as low down and dirty as me. That will have to come later. So I beg of you to consider me in choosing to whom this prize is going to belong.&quot;<br>
<br>
*salute*<br>
