<br>
Today, rumors came to my ears about a powerfull mask granting the illusion of gnome.<br>
For many halfsized are blue in their heart, even some among the so-called masters of the dark ways show some sentiments that are not suitable, and even worst, should bring the wrath of the things they call and venere as Gods upon them.<br>
Since this is obviously not the case, I will run the world searching this artifact and once I have find it, I will deceive those weaklings and show them your true power.<br>
Guide me in my quest Master...<br>
